{
  "stem": "5758.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we didn't sleep at all during the night, because [SIGHS] somewhere around in the region 11 or 12 o'clock at night we heard, in the courtyard, a noise of SS boots entering the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we saw the voices of our housekeeper, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw-- looking down from the window, we saw the [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "SR, ?] people in brown uniform with their swastika armband.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were talking to each other, and-- and they entered our entrance where we lived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can imagine how frightened we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- we heard a scream coming from the first floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On the first floor was a Jewish couple who was in the fashion business.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think their name was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- no, I'm sorry, that was another neighbor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No, it was Epstein, Epstein.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had a big sign on the outside notifying that this is a-- a firm, Epstein and-- and Bruder, Epstein and Bruder-- Brothers, [GERMAN], you know, fashion.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that scream from the-- came from the first floor where they lived, and we were on the third floor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And suddenly, we saw-- we heard a smash of a window and the-- a dump, a bump.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Somebody-- in fact, it was Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Epstein who hit the ground of the-- jumped from the first floor down to-- in the courtyard, and he was lying there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, the [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "SR ?] went off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the next day, I encountered [NON-ENGLISH], our housekeeper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He said to me, look, they had to have a Jew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I told him there's no other Jew here in that-- in that building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So they left after they did Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Epstein.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
